OL,7,F"We say he created a cycle whereby the
OL,8,Fvictims became dependant on him not
OL,9,Fonly to earn a living but as their
OL,10,Fsupplier of heroin.
OL,12,F"He was engaged in exploitative and
OL,13,Fmanipulative conduct to allow him to
OL,14,Fcommercially engage in prostitution."
OL,16,FThe barrister said the offending
OL,17,Fcontinued from 2015 until 2022 and
OL,18,Fwould have gone on but for
